{"id":1576,"date":"2023-08-14T23:05:56","date_gmt":"2023-08-14T16:05:56","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/thebloomhair.com\/?page_id=1576"},"modified":"2023-08-18T23:38:25","modified_gmt":"2023-08-18T16:38:25","slug":"how-to-order","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/thebloomhair.com\/how-to-order\/","title":{"rendered":"How to order"},"content":{"rendered":"\t<section class=\"section\" id=\"section_1126377120\">\n\t\t<div class=\"bg section-bg fill bg-fill  bg-loaded\" >\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t\n\n\t\t<div class=\"section-content relative\">\n\t\t\t\n<div class=\"row align-middle\"  id=\"row-41887867\">\n\n\t<div id=\"col-615946499\" class=\"col medium-5 small-12 large-5\"  >\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-inner\"  >\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n  <div class=\"banner has-hover\" id=\"banner-125495937\">\n          <div class=\"banner-inner fill\">\n        <div class=\"banner-bg fill\" >\n            <div class=\"bg fill bg-fill \"><\/div>\n                                    \n                    <\/div>\n\t\t\n        <div class=\"banner-layers container\">\n            <div class=\"fill banner-link\"><\/div>            \n        <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n\n            \n<style>\n#banner-125495937 {\n  padding-top: 400px;\n  background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\n}\n#banner-125495937 .bg.bg-loaded {\n  background-image: url(https:\/\/thebloomhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/mateus-campos-felipe-JoM_lC1WAnE-unsplash-731x1024.jpg);\n}\n#banner-125495937 .ux-shape-divider--top svg {\n  height: 150px;\n  --divider-top-width: 100%;\n}\n#banner-125495937 .ux-shape-divider--bottom svg {\n  height: 150px;\n  --divider-width: 100%;\n}\n@media (min-width:550px) {\n  #banner-125495937 {\n    padding-top: 600px;\n  }\n}\n<\/style>\n  <\/div>\n\n\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\n\n\t<div id=\"col-810775610\" class=\"col medium-7 small-12 large-7\"  >\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-inner\"  >\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t<div id=\"gap-780860510\" class=\"gap-element clearfix\" style=\"display:block; height:auto;\">\n\t\t\n<style>\n#gap-780860510 {\n  padding-top: 30px;\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/div>\n\t\n\t<div id=\"text-2725028517\" class=\"text\">\n\t\t\n<h3>How to order ? <\/h3>\n\t\t\n<style>\n#text-2725028517 {\n  font-size: 2.5rem;\n  line-height: 0.75;\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/div>\n\t\n<ul>\n<li>You text our hotline to discuss the order. Our\u00a0 sales will take care of you.\u00a0<\/li>\n<li>After you conclude the order with our sale, we will make invoices for you to check.<\/li>\n<li>After you check, you will pay all or deposit at least 50% to start the order.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>(For Nigeria, Ghana, Cameroon customers: We have agent to pay and shipping agent to your country. For other countries: payment is made by bank, WU, Moneygram, etc.)<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Process time for order from Vietnamese hair suppliers is about 7-14 days depending on orders.<\/li>\n<li>When the order is done, we will take pictures and videos of your order and send it to you to confirm.<\/li>\n<li>After you confirm everything in order, you balance the rest of the money then we will ship it to you (through agent or UPS, DHL, FedEx).<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\n<style>\n#col-810775610 > .col-inner {\n  padding: 0px 1% 0px 1%;\n}\n@media (min-width:550px) {\n  #col-810775610 > .col-inner {\n    padding: 0px 2% 0px 2%;\n  }\n}\n@media (min-width:850px) {\n  #col-810775610 > .col-inner {\n    padding: 0px 0px 0px 10%;\n  }\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/div>\n\n\t\n<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t\n<style>\n#section_1126377120 {\n  padding-top: 30px;\n  padding-bottom: 30px;\n}\n#section_1126377120 .ux-shape-divider--top svg {\n  height: 150px;\n  --divider-top-width: 100%;\n}\n#section_1126377120 .ux-shape-divider--bottom svg {\n  height: 150px;\n  --divider-width: 100%;\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/section>\n\t\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"","protected":false},"author":4,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_st